{"tid":1265193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大嶼山男子度假屋內燒炭亡","createTime":"2019-06-29T05:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T05:30:55.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f1828733e2f35a561ecee9f2ac7d1ced5c3df08a","tid":1265193,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T05:30:55.000Z","msg":"今早9時45分，大嶼山長沙下村，一名中年男子被發現在度假屋內燒炭，陷入昏迷，救護員接報到場，證實男事主當場死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方展開調查，初步了解現場兩層高的度假屋，是某集團所有，給員工租用。而屋內撿獲遺書，事主疑因病困擾，初步相信事件無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmqxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=87698398\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190629/59769890\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190629%2F59769890&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmqxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=034385a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190629%2F59769890&h=17d6d713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190629/59769890</a>"}]}